      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="541d5-102">呼び出し元の認証または承認を必要とする Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) アプリケーションを作成する場合は、セキュリティに関連するイベントを成功、失敗、またはその両方のいずれかに記録するように指定できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="541d5-102">When creating a Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) application that requires authentication and/or authorization of the callers, you can specify that events related to security be recorded for either success, failure, or both.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="541d5-103">監査レベルは、この列挙体によって決定されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="541d5-103">The level of auditing is determined by this enumeration.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="541d5-104">監査ログの場所は、<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior.AuditLogLocation%2A> クラスの <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior> プロパティを <xref:System.ServiceModel.AuditLogLocation> 値のいずれかに設定することで指定されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="541d5-104">The location of the audit log is specified by setting the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior.AuditLogLocation%2A> property of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior> class to one of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.AuditLogLocation> values.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="541d5-105">監査の詳細については、「[監査](/dotnet/framework/wcf/feature-details/auditing-security-events)」を参照してください。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="541d5-105">For more information about auditing, see [Auditing](/dotnet/framework/wcf/feature-details/auditing-security-events).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="541d5-106">[&lt;serviceSecurityAudit&gt;](/dotnet/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/wcf/servicesecurityaudit) binding を使用して監査動作を指定することもできます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="541d5-106">You can also specify audit behavior using the [&lt;serviceSecurityAudit&gt;](/dotnet/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/wcf/servicesecurityaudit) binding.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="541d5-107">次の例では、<xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior.MessageAuthenticationAuditLevel%2A> プロパティと <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior.ServiceAuthorizationAuditLevel%2A> プロパティを <xref:System.ServiceModel.AuditLevel> 値のいずれかに設定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="541d5-107">The following example sets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior.MessageAuthenticationAuditLevel%2A> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceSecurityAuditBehavior.ServiceAuthorizationAuditLevel%2A> properties to one of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.AuditLevel> values.</span></span>  
  
